headline: Cognizant (CTSH) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Cognizant (CTSH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +3.97% and +1.01%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
